          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "亲至寒窑探病，则见败瓦颓垣，菜羹粗粝，较之相府画栋雕梁，珍馐美味，不胜苦乐之感。王宝钏形容憔悴，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "见母大哭。夫人劝以同回相府，王宝钏坚执不允，夫人爱怜之极欲与女同居寒窑。王宝钏无奈，假允同归。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "诳夫人出窑紧闭双门，以示决绝。夫人叹息而去。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "根据《戏考》第二册整理"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（丫鬟引陈氏同上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "陈氏",
          "line_type": "引子",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "鹤发皓首，两鬓如霜。"
        },
        {
          "character": "陈氏",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "夫为相国伴皇家，妻沾雨露享荣华。终朝只把娇儿叹，哪得周全喜生花。"
        },
        {
          "character": "陈氏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "老身陈氏，配夫王允。膝下无儿，所生三女：长女金钏，许配苏龙；次女银钏，"
        },
        {
          "character": "陈氏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "许配魏虎；三女宝钏，配夫平贵。可恨三女性情高傲，居住城南，老身百般"
        },
        {
          "character": "陈氏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "相劝，执意不肯回府。今早也曾命家院去往城南，探望三女度日光景如何。这"
        },
        {
          "character": "陈氏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "时候怎么还不见回来？"
        },
        {
          "character": "陈氏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "丫鬟伺候了！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（家院上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "家院",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "有事即来报，无事不乱言。"
        },
        {
          "character": "家院",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "参见老夫人。"
        },
        {
          "character": "陈氏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "罢了，起来。命你打听三姑娘，光景如何？"
        },
        {
          "character": "家院",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "三姑娘在窑中身染重病。"
        },
        {
          "character": "陈氏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你待怎讲？"
        },
        {
          "character": "家院",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "三姑娘身染重病！"
        },
        {
          "character": "陈氏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哎呀，儿吓！"
        },
        {
          "character": "陈氏",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "听得家院一声禀，"
        },
        {
          "character": "陈氏",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "烈性的三女病缠身。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（哭板） 眼望城南高声叫，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我的儿吓……"
        },
        {
          "character": "陈氏",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "怎能够到寒窑探望儿身。"
        },
        {
          "character": "家院",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "老夫人不必啼哭，何不多带银米衣裳，去往寒窑探望三姑娘。"
        },
        {
          "character": "陈氏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "言之有理。家院、丫鬟，多带银米衣裳与你三姑娘。家院，吩咐外面车辆伺候。"
        },
        {
          "character": "家院",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "车辆走上。"
        },
        {
          "character": "陈氏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "儿吓！"
        },
        {
          "character": "陈氏",
          "line_type": "西皮慢板",
          "musical_style": "西皮慢板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "叫家院你与我前把路引，"
        },
        {
          "character": "陈氏",
          "line_type": "西皮慢板",
          "musical_style": "西皮慢板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "想从前大不该彩楼结亲。"
        },
        {
          "character": "陈氏",
          "line_type": "西皮慢板",
          "musical_style": "西皮慢板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "为女儿与相国吵闹相争；"
        },
        {
          "character": "陈氏",
          "line_type": "西皮慢板",
          "musical_style": "西皮慢板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "为女儿哭得我头闷眼昏。"
        },
        {
          "character": "陈氏",
          "line_type": "西皮慢板",
          "musical_style": "西皮慢板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "宝钏儿受凄凉一十七春。"
        },
        {
          "character": "陈氏",
          "line_type": "西皮慢板",
          "musical_style": "西皮慢板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "为宝钏把我的精神用尽"
        },
        {
          "character": "陈氏",
          "line_type": "西皮慢板",
          "musical_style": "西皮慢板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "为宝钏常忧闷神昏不定"
        },
        {
          "character": "陈氏",
          "line_type": "西皮慢板",
          "musical_style": "西皮慢板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "实可叹薛平郎西凉丧命"
        },
        {
          "character": "家院",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "老夫人，此地已是寒窑。"
        },
        {
          "character": "陈氏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "前去叫门。"
        },
        {
          "character": "家院",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "三姑娘开门来。"
        },
        {
          "character": "王宝钏",
          "line_type": "内白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "来了。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（王宝钏上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "王宝钏",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "忽听窑外有人声，"
        },
        {
          "character": "王宝钏",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "想必是四邻探奴身。"
        },
        {
          "character": "王宝钏",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "寒窑内哭坏女钗裙。"
        },
        {
          "character": "王宝钏",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "薛郎一去无音信"
        },
        {
          "character": "家院",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "三姑娘开门来，老夫人来了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "王宝钏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哎呀！"
        },
        {
          "character": "王宝钏",
          "line_type": "西皮流水板",
          "musical_style": "西皮流水板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "老娘来到城南郡，"
        },
        {
          "character": "王宝钏",
          "line_type": "西皮流水板",
          "musical_style": "西皮流水板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "好一似钢刀刺在心。"
        },
        {
          "character": "王宝钏",
          "line_type": "西皮流水板",
          "musical_style": "西皮流水板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "这回怎见老娘亲？"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（王宝钏开窑，出窑。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "王宝钏",
          "line_type": "叫头",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "母亲！"
        },
        {
          "character": "陈氏",
          "line_type": "叫头",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "宝钏！"
        },
        {
          "character": "王宝钏",
          "line_type": "叫头",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "老娘！"
        },
        {
          "character": "陈氏",
          "line_type": "叫头",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我儿！"
        },
        {
          "character": "王宝钏",
          "line_type": "哭",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "老娘亲吓！"
        },
        {
          "character": "陈氏",
          "line_type": "哭",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哎呀，儿吓！"
        },
        {
          "character": "陈氏",
          "line_type": "西皮导板",
          "musical_style": "西皮导板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "一见娇儿珠泪滚，"
        },
        {
          "character": "陈氏",
          "line_type": "哭",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "三女，宝钏儿吓！"
        },
        {
          "character": "陈氏",
          "line_type": "西皮流水板",
          "musical_style": "西皮流水板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "手搀三女说分明："
        },
        {
          "character": "陈氏",
          "line_type": "西皮流水板",
          "musical_style": "西皮流水板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "乖巧伶俐甚聪明。"
        },
        {
          "character": "陈氏",
          "line_type": "西皮流水板",
          "musical_style": "西皮流水板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "闷来花园散精神。"
        },
        {
          "character": "陈氏",
          "line_type": "西皮流水板",
          "musical_style": "西皮流水板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "许多丫鬟随后跟。"
        },
        {
          "character": "陈氏",
          "line_type": "西皮流水板",
          "musical_style": "西皮流水板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "母女分别十七春。"
        },
        {
          "character": "陈氏",
          "line_type": "西皮流水板",
          "musical_style": "西皮流水板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "今朝我儿变了形。"
        },
        {
          "character": "陈氏",
          "line_type": "西皮流水板",
          "musical_style": "西皮流水板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "忍饥受饱不回心。"
        },
        {
          "character": "陈氏",
          "line_type": "西皮流水板",
          "musical_style": "西皮流水板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "晚来好似一孤灯。"
        },
        {
          "character": "陈氏",
          "line_type": "西皮流水板",
          "musical_style": "西皮流水板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "破窑怎藏儿的身？"
        },
        {
          "character": "陈氏",
          "line_type": "西皮流水板",
          "musical_style": "西皮流水板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "叫娘心疼不心疼！"
        },
        {
          "character": "陈氏",
          "line_type": "西皮流水板",
          "musical_style": "西皮流水板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "儿在相府多侥幸"
        },
        {
          "character": "陈氏",
          "line_type": "西皮流水板",
          "musical_style": "西皮流水板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "闲来绣阁挑花朵"
        },
        {
          "character": "陈氏",
          "line_type": "西皮流水板",
          "musical_style": "西皮流水板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "多少侍女来陪伴"
        },
        {
          "character": "陈氏",
          "line_type": "西皮流水板",
          "musical_style": "西皮流水板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "自从我儿出相府"
        },
        {
          "character": "陈氏",
          "line_type": "西皮流水板",
          "musical_style": "西皮流水板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "从前娇容如嫩笋"
        },
        {
          "character": "陈氏",
          "line_type": "西皮流水板",
          "musical_style": "西皮流水板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "面黄肌瘦容颜改"
        },
        {
          "character": "陈氏",
          "line_type": "西皮流水板",
          "musical_style": "西皮流水板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "日见无人来谈论"
        },
        {
          "character": "陈氏",
          "line_type": "西皮流水板",
          "musical_style": "西皮流水板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "寒风冷凉儿受尽"
        },
        {
          "character": "陈氏",
          "line_type": "西皮流水板",
          "musical_style": "西皮流水板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "你本是宰相千金女"
        },
        {
          "character": "王宝钏",
          "line_type": "西皮二六板",
          "musical_style": "西皮二六板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "老娘不必两泪淋，"
        },
        {
          "character": "王宝钏",
          "line_type": "西皮二六板",
          "musical_style": "西皮二六板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "女儿言来听分明："
        },
        {
          "character": "王宝钏",
          "line_type": "西皮二六板",
          "musical_style": "西皮二六板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "许配为官做宦人。"
        },
        {
          "character": "王宝钏",
          "line_type": "西皮二六板",
          "musical_style": "西皮二六板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "彩球单打花郎身。"
        },
        {
          "character": "王宝钏",
          "line_type": "西皮二六板",
          "musical_style": "西皮二六板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "富的富来贫的贫。"
        },
        {
          "character": "王宝钏",
          "line_type": "西皮二六板",
          "musical_style": "西皮二六板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "谁做耕田种地人？"
        },
        {
          "character": "王宝钏",
          "line_type": "西皮二六板",
          "musical_style": "西皮二六板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "大姐"
        },
        {
          "character": "王宝钏",
          "line_type": "西皮二六板",
          "musical_style": "西皮二六板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "二姐有福分"
        },
        {
          "character": "王宝钏",
          "line_type": "西皮二六板",
          "musical_style": "西皮二六板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "惟有女儿命内苦"
        },
        {
          "character": "王宝钏",
          "line_type": "西皮二六板",
          "musical_style": "西皮二六板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "好的好来歹的歹"
        },
        {
          "character": "王宝钏",
          "line_type": "西皮二六板",
          "musical_style": "西皮二六板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "若人多想为官宦"
        },
        {
          "character": "陈氏",
          "line_type": "西皮流水板",
          "musical_style": "西皮流水板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "背地里只把相国恨，"
        },
        {
          "character": "陈氏",
          "line_type": "西皮流水板",
          "musical_style": "西皮流水板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "三个女儿两看承。"
        },
        {
          "character": "陈氏",
          "line_type": "西皮流水板",
          "musical_style": "西皮流水板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "唯有冤家我心疼。"
        },
        {
          "character": "陈氏",
          "line_type": "西皮流水板",
          "musical_style": "西皮流水板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "瓦上霜来风前灯。"
        },
        {
          "character": "陈氏",
          "line_type": "西皮流水板",
          "musical_style": "西皮流水板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "好似枯木又逢春。"
        },
        {
          "character": "陈氏",
          "line_type": "西皮流水板",
          "musical_style": "西皮流水板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "大女"
        },
        {
          "character": "陈氏",
          "line_type": "西皮流水板",
          "musical_style": "西皮流水板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "二女我不爱"
        },
        {
          "character": "陈氏",
          "line_type": "西皮流水板",
          "musical_style": "西皮流水板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "老身今年六十九"
        },
        {
          "character": "陈氏",
          "line_type": "西皮流水板",
          "musical_style": "西皮流水板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "今日见了娇儿面"
        },
        {
          "character": "王宝钏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "母亲请上，待女儿拜见。"
        },
        {
          "character": "陈氏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "儿不要拜了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "王宝钏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "儿久离膝下，少奉甘旨，望母亲恕罪！"
        },
        {
          "character": "陈氏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我儿起来。"
        },
        {
          "character": "陈氏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "家院、丫鬟，见过你三姑娘。"
        },
        {
          "character": "家院、丫鬟",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "参见三姑娘！"
        },
        {
          "character": "王宝钏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "罢了！"
        },
        {
          "character": "王宝钏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "母亲不在相府，来至寒窑则甚？"
        },
        {
          "character": "陈氏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "家院回府：报道吾儿身染重病。此病从何而起？"
        },
        {
          "character": "王宝钏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "多因魏虎打从寒窑经过，言道儿丈夫命丧西凉，爹爹又差人前来劝奴改嫁，儿"
        },
        {
          "character": "王宝钏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "闻此言，因此身体十分病重。今日母亲到此，该是儿的病，好了一半了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "陈氏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哦，我把你这老天杀的，常常逼我儿改嫁，此番回去，又要与他吵闹一场！"
        },
        {
          "character": "王宝钏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "吓，母亲，为了女儿，不要伤了你二老的和气。"
        },
        {
          "character": "陈氏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "儿吓，为娘看在我儿分上，不与你父吵闹就是。"
        },
        {
          "character": "王宝钏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "多谢母亲。"
        },
        {
          "character": "陈氏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "儿吓，为娘要进窑内看看，我儿的度日光景如何？"
        },
        {
          "character": "王宝钏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "寒窑窄小，不看也罢了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "陈氏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "咳，我儿住了一十七载，难道为娘就进去不得么？"
        },
        {
          "character": "王宝钏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "如此待女儿打扫打扫。"
        },
        {
          "character": "陈氏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "不用打扫，与为娘带路进窑，儿吓！"
        },
        {
          "character": "陈氏",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "雕梁画阁儿不住，"
        },
        {
          "character": "陈氏",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "寒窑怎存我儿身？"
        },
        {
          "character": "王宝钏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哎，母亲请用。"
        },
        {
          "character": "陈氏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哎呀！"
        },
        {
          "character": "陈氏",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "珍馐海味儿不用，"
        },
        {
          "character": "陈氏",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "罐内稀饭怎度光阴？"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "陈氏 （同三叫头） （母亲）（宝钏）！（老娘）（我儿）！哎吓，（老娘亲）（儿吓）！"
        },
        {
          "character": "陈氏",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "哭一声王宝钏！"
        },
        {
          "character": "王宝钏",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "叫一声老娘亲！"
        },
        {
          "character": "陈氏",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "想当年在相府何等侥幸，"
        },
        {
          "character": "陈氏",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "到如今住寒窑娘好心痛。"
        },
        {
          "character": "王宝钏",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "只当孩儿伤了命，"
        },
        {
          "character": "王宝钏",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "何劳娘亲挂在心？"
        },
        {
          "character": "陈氏",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "儿随为娘回相府，"
        },
        {
          "character": "陈氏",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "只享荣华不愁贫。"
        },
        {
          "character": "王宝钏",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "儿与爹爹三击掌，"
        },
        {
          "character": "王宝钏",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "饿死寒窑不进相府门。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "陈氏 （哭板） 王宝钏……"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "王宝钏 （哭板） 老娘亲……"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "王宝钏 （同哭板） 呀吓呀吓！"
        },
        {
          "character": "陈氏",
          "line_type": "哭",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我的儿吓……"
        },
        {
          "character": "王宝钏",
          "line_type": "哭",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "老娘亲吓……"
        },
        {
          "character": "王宝钏",
          "line_type": "西皮导板",
          "musical_style": "西皮导板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "老娘亲请上容儿拜禀，"
        },
        {
          "character": "陈氏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我儿不必拜了，一旁坐了。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（家院、丫鬟同暗下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "王宝钏",
          "line_type": "西皮慢板",
          "musical_style": "西皮慢板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "母女们在寒窑叙一叙苦情："
        },
        {
          "character": "王宝钏",
          "line_type": "西皮慢板",
          "musical_style": "西皮慢板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "女儿在后花园把香来焚。"
        },
        {
          "character": "王宝钏",
          "line_type": "西皮慢板",
          "musical_style": "西皮慢板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "后宫娘娘得知情。"
        },
        {
          "character": "王宝钏",
          "line_type": "西皮慢板",
          "musical_style": "西皮慢板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "绣成了彩球定终身。"
        },
        {
          "character": "王宝钏",
          "line_type": "西皮慢板",
          "musical_style": "西皮慢板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "谁知单打在花郎身。"
        },
        {
          "character": "王宝钏",
          "line_type": "西皮慢板",
          "musical_style": "西皮慢板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "老爹爹一见怒气升。"
        },
        {
          "character": "王宝钏",
          "line_type": "西皮慢板",
          "musical_style": "西皮慢板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "后门赶出女儿身。"
        },
        {
          "character": "王宝钏",
          "line_type": "西皮慢板",
          "musical_style": "西皮慢板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "破瓦寒窑把身存。"
        },
        {
          "character": "王宝钏",
          "line_type": "西皮慢板",
          "musical_style": "西皮慢板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "红鬃烈马乱伤人。"
        },
        {
          "character": "王宝钏",
          "line_type": "西皮慢板",
          "musical_style": "西皮慢板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "唐王驾前去讨封。"
        },
        {
          "character": "王宝钏",
          "line_type": "西皮慢板",
          "musical_style": "西皮慢板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "平贵倒做马先行。"
        },
        {
          "character": "王宝钏",
          "line_type": "西皮慢板",
          "musical_style": "西皮慢板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "儿比孤雁失了群。"
        },
        {
          "character": "王宝钏",
          "line_type": "西皮慢板",
          "musical_style": "西皮慢板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "休把孩儿挂在心。"
        },
        {
          "character": "王宝钏",
          "line_type": "西皮慢板",
          "musical_style": "西皮慢板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "都只为老娘亲身染重病"
        },
        {
          "character": "王宝钏",
          "line_type": "西皮慢板",
          "musical_style": "西皮慢板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "许愿降香三年整"
        },
        {
          "character": "王宝钏",
          "line_type": "西皮慢板",
          "musical_style": "西皮慢板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "恩赐五彩花绒线"
        },
        {
          "character": "王宝钏",
          "line_type": "西皮慢板",
          "musical_style": "西皮慢板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "实指望打中宦门后"
        },
        {
          "character": "王宝钏",
          "line_type": "西皮慢板",
          "musical_style": "西皮慢板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "夫妻二人相府进"
        },
        {
          "character": "王宝钏",
          "line_type": "西皮慢板",
          "musical_style": "西皮慢板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "前门赶出薛平贵"
        },
        {
          "character": "王宝钏",
          "line_type": "西皮慢板",
          "musical_style": "西皮慢板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "夫妻二人无投奔"
        },
        {
          "character": "王宝钏",
          "line_type": "西皮慢板",
          "musical_style": "西皮慢板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "渠江河内妖魔显"
        },
        {
          "character": "王宝钏",
          "line_type": "西皮慢板",
          "musical_style": "西皮慢板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "平贵擒了红鬃马"
        },
        {
          "character": "王宝钏",
          "line_type": "西皮慢板",
          "musical_style": "西皮慢板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "西凉贼子造了反"
        },
        {
          "character": "王宝钏",
          "line_type": "西皮慢板",
          "musical_style": "西皮慢板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "一去不觉十七载"
        },
        {
          "character": "王宝钏",
          "line_type": "西皮慢板",
          "musical_style": "西皮慢板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "老娘回府对父论"
        },
        {
          "character": "陈氏",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "我儿不必心烦闷，"
        },
        {
          "character": "陈氏",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "不要啼哭费精神。"
        },
        {
          "character": "陈氏",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "不要牵挂平郎身。"
        },
        {
          "character": "陈氏",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "跟娘坐来随娘行。"
        },
        {
          "character": "陈氏",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "舍生忘死拼他人。"
        },
        {
          "character": "陈氏",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "儿就是披麻戴孝人。"
        },
        {
          "character": "陈氏",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "不要听你父的话"
        },
        {
          "character": "陈氏",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "儿随为娘回相府"
        },
        {
          "character": "陈氏",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "倘若你父有谈论"
        },
        {
          "character": "陈氏",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "若是为娘归泉路"
        },
        {
          "character": "王宝钏",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "老娘亲不必两泪淋，"
        },
        {
          "character": "王宝钏",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "女儿言来听分明："
        },
        {
          "character": "王宝钏",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "儿是披麻戴孝人；"
        },
        {
          "character": "王宝钏",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "女儿不去哭半声。"
        },
        {
          "character": "王宝钏",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "儿要修修来世身。"
        },
        {
          "character": "王宝钏",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "倘若老娘身亡故"
        },
        {
          "character": "王宝钏",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "倘若爹爹身亡故"
        },
        {
          "character": "王宝钏",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "宝钏烧香把佛敬"
        },
        {
          "character": "陈氏",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "立志守节拿得稳，"
        },
        {
          "character": "陈氏",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "皇天不负你这苦心人。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（家院、丫鬟同暗上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "陈氏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "家院、丫鬟，将银米衣裳，交与你三姑娘。"
        },
        {
          "character": "王宝钏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "且慢，相府之物，一概不要。"
        },
        {
          "character": "陈氏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "儿吓，你不收下，岂不辜负为娘一片好心？儿吓，收下罢！"
        },
        {
          "character": "王宝钏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "多谢母亲！"
        },
        {
          "character": "陈氏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "这便才是。"
        },
        {
          "character": "陈氏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "家院、丫鬟，你们暂且回去，老身在此陪伴你三姑娘一宵，明日回府。"
        },
        {
          "character": "王宝钏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "吓，母亲，寒窑肮脏得紧，母亲焉能得住？"
        },
        {
          "character": "陈氏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我儿住得，难道为娘就住不得么？"
        },
        {
          "character": "王宝钏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "且住，母亲不回相府，这便如何是好？我自有道理。"
        },
        {
          "character": "王宝钏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "吓，母亲，女儿情愿回转相府去了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "陈氏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "好，我儿情愿回得相府了！"
        },
        {
          "character": "陈氏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "家院吩咐车辆搭上。"
        },
        {
          "character": "陈氏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我儿开了窑门。"
        },
        {
          "character": "王宝钏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "是。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（陈氏、家院、丫鬟同出窑，王宝钏关窑门。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "陈氏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "儿吓，为何将窑门紧闭？"
        },
        {
          "character": "王宝钏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "啊吓，母亲哪！儿与爹爹三击掌，饿在寒窑……也是不回去的了！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "陈氏 （哭板） 儿吓，狠心的儿，不把娘来送！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "王宝钏 （哭板） 娘吓，儿跪寒窑送娘亲。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "陈氏 （哭板） 娘哭儿来天地震！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "王宝钏 （哭板） 儿哭娘来泪成冰！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "陈氏 （哭板） 我那狠心的王三姐！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "王宝钏 （哭板） 我那疼儿的老娘亲……吓……"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "陈氏 （哭板） 啊……啊……啊……啊……我的儿吓……"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "王宝钏 （哭板） 啊吓……儿的老娘亲吓……吓……吓……吓……"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（众人同下。）"
        }
      ],
